name: JAM Token
description: JAMTOKEN - Made by a community of Jab- Handed Jammers! A perpetual contest between tastes; A MasterClass on how to do memecoins right! Jam Token was conceived by a community of like-minded people with a wide array of skills. Community Working Game dApp with weekly variation JAMM3D Game - Jam Shooter allows players to choose between Berry, Grape, Peach, or Orange Jams The Reward - At the end of each week, the team with the highest score get a surprise bonus! How it works? Once players' wallets are signed by a specific Jam type, they start racking up points!
